GALLERY:
Create a collection of images that can be displayed in a fancy gallery.

TAGS:
gallery, Render the gallery with the images
    'name' Name of the gallery you want to display
        String
    'max' Maximum number of images to show
        Int, optional
galleryindex, Show a list of all galleries
    'withImages' Also load the images
        Boolean, optional